OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny isolated
OL,6,Fthundery showers soon clearing, then
OL,7,Fsome clearer skies. Clouding over with
OL,8,Fthe chance of some light showers
OL,9,Fcrossing from the west during the
OL,10,Fearly hours. Overnight temperatures
OL,11,Fremaining very warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,14,Feastwards during Sunday, with sunny
OL,15,Fspells for much of the day, especially
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon. More seasonable
OL,17,Ftemperatures expected. Winds moderate
OL,18,Fsouthwesterly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
